  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK523">
<l>aḷavaḷā villātāṉ vāḻkkai kuḷavaḷāk </l>
<l> kōṭiṉṟi nīrniṟain taṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The wealth of one who does not mingle freely with his relatives, will be like the filling of water in a spacious tank that has no banks.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
